1604206800.title: Managing Asia
1604206800.descr: Managing Asia is a series of in-depth conversations with some of the most influential business leaders in Asia today, who are changing the business landscape on the continent. Join host Christine Tan, as she interviews CEOs and entrepreneurs about various issues, as well as their professional inspirations and goals.

1604208600.title: Finding Solutions: Goalkeepers
1604208600.descr: CNBC's magazine explores issues considering racial equality, work diversity and inclusion all over the world. The programme brings the latest news stories dealing with these serious themes. It also includes experts' debates on these problems, as they try to come up with the best possible solutions for them.

1604210400.title: American Greed: Fraudster Of the Opera / Frozen Assets-the Ice Capers
1604210400.descr: American Greed is a documentary series focussing on the largest white-collar crimes, also known as financial or corporate crimes, throughout the history of America. We explore the lengths these opportunistic scam artists go to for their own personal gain. The masterminds behind theses flawed plans certainly learn one thing; crime doesn't pay. Narrated by American actor Stacy Keach.

1604214000.title: Joel Osteen: Jo859 – Grass In the Desert
1604214000.descr: Hear the messages of hope that best-selling author, evangelist and the senior pastor of Lakewood Church, Joel Osteen is delivering in each episode. Joel's positive and encouraging speeches will allow viewers to hear God's message of hope, love and victory and be inspired to do great things in life.

1604215800.title: Answers With Bayless Conley (f)
1604215800.descr: In this religious television show Pastor Bayless Conley of the Cottonwood Christian Center, explains how religion can be used as a solution for various issues. Join him as he talks about the practical teachings of the Bible, while addressing serious problems, including depression and addiction.

1604217600.title: In Touch Ministries
1604217600.descr: In Touch Ministries is a long-running television series in which senior pastor of the First Baptist Church in Atlanta, Dr Charles Stanley, shares lessons about the Christian faith. He discusses various themes, such as family, prayer, motherhood and fear, addressing stories from the Bible and offering a deeper understanding of Christian teachings.

1604219400.title: New Creation Church With Joseph Prince: Victory In Your Day Of Trouble
1604219400.descr: Religious programme with spiritual messages on life and faith, religious interpretations and words of praise and worship. Hosted by Joseph Prince, the senior pastor and co-founder of the New Creation Church in Singapore – a large non-denominational Christian church in Asia. With his energetic and sometimes humorous style, Joseph Prince has spoken to live audiences across the world and his sermons are broadcast globally.

1604224800.title: Air Travel In Turmoil

1604239200.title: Tonight Show
1604239200.descr: Jimmy Fallon has been hosting this well known, late night talk show since early 2014, and shows no signs of slowing down. The seventh version of NBC's franchise, the Tonight Show, Fallon's slot has proved one of the most popular. Featuring guest interviews, musical performances, comedic sketches and entertaining games, the show has proved catalyst for viral videos.

1604246400.title: Meet the Press
1604246400.descr: American current affairs programme with indepth interviews and roundtable discussion and analysis. The world's longest running television show interviews key players from the worlds of politics, economics, foreign affairs and other areas of public interest. With 13 moderators over its 70 years of broadcasting, it has interviewed the world's most important politicians and political players.
